@shubham1g5 Just noticed one thing. This particular method parseUpdateToPrompt is being called from both attemptCczUpdateParse and attemptApkUpdateParse.
But for both of them we're using setLatestCommcareVersion when we should've used setLatestAppVersion as well.
I'm not sure about the actual impact of this bug, but seems like we should fix this in this release. Can you please check?

